query:
SELECT 
  c.id,
  c.dataConsulta,
  c.igSemanas,
  c.igDias,
  c.igDumSemanas,
  c.igDumDias,
  c.igUltrassomSemanas,
  c.igUltrassomDias,
  g.nome,
  g.dum,
  g.dataUltrassom,
  g.igUltrassomSemanas as g_igUsSemanas,
  g.igUltrassomDias as g_igUsDias
FROM consultasPrenatal c
JOIN gestantes g ON c.gestanteId = g.id
WHERE g.nome LIKE '%Adrieli%'
ORDER BY c.dataConsulta DESC
LIMIT 5;
